item.title: Prayer bpn13085 in Daga
item.description: Nop ma nainit wamewa gapan waen ge apan mu dere, waenapan dere den wagup namumup yona wain, ma yogup kanamawa gwanap wan. (Kitáb-i-Aqdas) “Nu uruga, Ipiwa gapan Maman iup mega ae amat tait.” (Source category: Nainit (Wedding Vow)) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13085)
